It is summarized by the following categories: 1) Individual pesticide chemical or groups of chemicals or all chemicals 2) Individual application site(crop) or group of sites(crops) or all sites(crops) 3) Individual county or all counties 4) Multiple years start from year 1991 to year 2009, and it is continuously updated 5) Measures of pesticide usage by Gross Pounds, or pesticide application intensity by Application Rate (Pounds per Acre Treated), or by Acre Treated.</dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>pesticide</dcat:keyword>         <dcat:keyword>chemicals</dcat:keyword>
